As cities evolve and advance, the need to urbanize without compromising future generations is vital. The panelists, Cherrie D Atilano, Chief Executive Officer of AGREA Agricultural Systems International and Co-Founder of Nagrika Tarun Sharma, share how can we embark on sustainable urban development in an inclusive way.

